---
title: Thai Green Pumpkin & Broccoli Curry with Roasted Peanuts
description: This pumpkin and broccoli curry is a little bit sweet, a little bit spicy, a little bit salty and totally delicious! It’s packed with veggie goodness and sprinkled with roasted peanuts for extra flavour and crunch. Dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-green-pumpkin-broccoli-curry-cf3d1165.jpg
